title: 04/13/2021 - Hour 2 - Aaron Rodgers Will Get Out of Green Bay
itunes:title: 04/13/2021 - Hour 2 - Aaron Rodgers Will Get Out of Green Bay
description:
Jason Smith and Jason McIntyre are in for Dan and the Danettes, reacting to Reggie Miller saying he would’ve told Michael Jordan to go F himself if he asked to team up. The guys agree Aaron Rodgers is waiting for his time to 'strike' and ask for a trade from the Packers. Plus, Luka Doncic bashes the idea of an NBA play-in.
